Title: Apple Watch - Series 5 Glass Repair
Body (HTML):
Apple Watch - Series 5 Glass Repair

 

The Apple Watch - Series 5 has great build quality and design, but it isn't invincible. Since your device is of little use when broken, it's a good idea to bring it to iFixYouri for expert Glass Repair.

 

Each device has its own lifespan - some devices use higher quality components than others and can last years if properly maintained. Drops, water or liquid, even a jolt can damage your device.

Those who have both cracked glass and a broken LCD should opt for our Apple Watch - Series 5 Glass & LCD Repair. This service is for glass breakage only.

 

After checkout, you'll receive an email confirmation and shipping label. When your phone arrives at our repair center, we do diagnostic tests to determine if any other issues are at play. Outgoing testing ensures that your Apple Watch - Series 5 is fully functional. With the repairs complete, we send you a tracking number and ship your Apple Watch - Series 5 back to you!

 

Free UPS ground shipping and $100 of insurance are included. You may purchase faster shipping options and additional insurance protection using the drop-down options above. That's up to you. Don't send us your cables, charges, or cases please. We have plenty here already :) Just package your Apple Watch - Series 5 in a secure box and affix the provided label.

 

Glass Repair repair includes a 90-day warranty that covers all but accidental damage. If you notice something off about the fit, function, or performance of your replacement part or parts, let us know right away and we will be glad to help.

 

If you have specific questions about Glass Repair or any Apple Watch - Series 5 service from iFixYouri, please ask them in the box below. Contact customer service with any questions at 888-494-4349 or support@ifixyouri.com.
